   Equipped with both shoulder and hand straps for easy handling and carrying Product Dimensions:- 74 x 28 x 17 cm (29.13 x 11.02 x 6.69 inches), Weight: 650 grams (0.65 kg) Package Contents:- Amazon Brand - Solimo Badminton Kit Bag, Rapid; Colour: Blue   Show More
product_description: Store and carry your badminton gear without any hassle with the Solimo Badminton Kit Bag, Rapid. The outside of the badminton kit bag is manufactured using water-repellent polyester fabric, while the inside is made using polyester fabric. The badminton kit bag undergoes nineteen product tests to ensure sturdiness, durability, and the bag's quality. For secure opening and closing, this blue-hued badminton kit bag is equipped with a high-quality zipper tested for 500 cycles. The Solimo Badminton Kit Bag, Rapid, has two compartments that spaciously accommodate two sets of racquets, and additional space for storing shuttlecock, bottle, extra clothing, and more. Comprising ample space, the badminton kit bag is the perfect choice for keeping your badminton gear such as racquet sets, water bottle, pair of clothes, shoes, keys, shuttlecock, fitness items like bands, grips, and other such things. The provision of the sturdy shoulder and hand straps allow you to carry the bag effortlessly, wherever you go.
